<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>{% block title %}Welcome!{% endblock %}</title>
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@400..700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 128 128%22><text y=%221.2em%22 font-size=%2296%22>⚫️</text><text y=%221.3em%22 x=%220.2em%22 font-size=%2276%22 fill=%22%23fff%22>sf</text></svg>">
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">
        {% block stylesheets %}
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-z3gLpd7yknf1YoNbCzqRKc4qyor8gaKU1qmn+CShxbuBusANI9QpRohGBreCFkKxLhei6S9CQXFEbbKuqLg0DA==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
        {% endblock %}

        {% block javascripts %}
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        {% block importmap %}{{ importmap('app') }}{% endblock %}
        {% endblock %}
    </head>
    <body>        
        {% block body %}{% endblock %}
        <script src="{{ asset('assets/js/script.js') }}"></script>
    </body>
    <footer>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mt-4 mb-4">
        <!-- Button trigger modal -->
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary me-1" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#exampleModal">
        Mes informations
        </button>
        <!-- Modal -->
        <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="exampleModalLabel">Plus d'informations</h1>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>Je suis actuellement en formation développeur web & web mobile a l'AFPA de Saint-Jean-de-vedas de Septembre 2025 jusqu'à Mai 2026. </p>
                <p>Passionné par le développement web et la création de sites internet, je suis à la recherche d'un stage pratique pour mettre en application les compétences acquises durant ma formation. </p>
                <p>Rigoureux, motivé et curieux, je suis prêt à relever de nouveaux défis et à contribuer activement aux projets de votre entreprise.</p>
                <a href="https://github.com/TersigniKev" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"> Mon GitHub</i></a>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
        <a href="uploads/Tersigni_Kevin.pdf" download class="download-btn">
            Télécharger mon CV
        </a>
    </div>
    </footer>
</html>
